  "description": {
    "zh": "好了，又一个新订单，这次需要更多注射器。这应该是来自这个特定买家的最后一笔订单，但如果他再订购更多，我也不会介意。\n\n现在他在寻找更稀有的注射器，也许可以去TerraGroupTerraGroup集团的实验室里看看可能会是个不错的主意？决定去哪里寻找这些针剂是你的事，有很多地方可以检查，但记住，高风险高回报。",
    "en": "Okay, a new order, even more injectors this time. It should be last order from this specific buyer, but I wouldn't mind if he ordered more.\n\nSo he's looking for even rarer injectors now, so paying a visit to the Terragroup laboratory might be a good idea? You decide where you will look for them, there are enough places you can check out, but remember, high risk high reward."
  },
